data.actual_result: Duplicate audit logs at random timing order shows.
data.expected_result: There shouldn't be any duplicated results, and the timeline should be in order from the most recent to the oldest.
data.short_description: Some audit log contents shows duplicate results, in order of wrong timing.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to audit logs. - Select "Filter by Action", and select "Kick Member" or "Ban Member" (These two are the ones that shows for me). - Notice your results. Some of the logs are duplicated, and ordered in wrong timing. (It may help if your filter doesn't have that many results). - Just a notice: This may not be only limited to Kick and Ban, it can happen elsewhere. Please try other filters as well.
